name: Language
comment:
This library provides a union type for languges for which Github provides color codes and their respective color

@docs Language, fromString, toColor

types.name: Language
types.comment: The union type of all languages supported by Github

values.name: fromString
values.comment: Parse a string to a lanuge. Unrecognized strings get turned into Other

values.name: toColor
values.comment: Convert a languges to its respective color code
